{"tid":2494563,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）瓏門一房710萬成交","createTime":"2021-04-18T16:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T10:23:47.000Z","uid":101341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1efa5873df2f97d62680a593f40b7366badf78","tid":2494563,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:00:46.000Z","msg":"樓市小陽春持續多月，消化不少購買力，雖然交投放緩，但市場仍不乏新高價。新地（016）屯門御海灣II高價開售，首批單位折實平均呎價超過1.8萬元，貴絕屯門新盤，即時辣㷫同區二手。其中屯門站上蓋瓏門，1房造價首次700萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中原地產酈偉倫表示，瓏門8座高層G室，實用面積379方呎，屬1房間隔，由於單位有租客居住中，即使買家不能睇樓，但仍能以高達710萬元成交，呎價18,734元，成為屋苑1房新樓王，買家為外區投資者。原業主2017年3月以548萬元購入，單位4年升值近3成。翻查成交紀錄，瓏門對上最貴1房為同座低10層G室，去年底以668萬元成交，最新成交較4個月前紀錄再推高42萬元或6.3%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210418/F3FZ3WTCPFENLHTZMTCMVNROU4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210418%2FF3FZ3WTCPFENLHTZMTCMVNROU4%2F&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=0de0f97d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210418%2FF3FZ3WTCPFENLHTZMTCMVNROU4%2F&h=a138c15a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210418/F3FZ3WTCPFENLHTZMTCMVNROU4/</a>"},{"pid":"ef473538e40fc28d0af3ed686f0b887c5d2f9283","tid":2494563,"uid":185631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"真好！ <br />\n有人托住個市俾香港人賣樓移民！"},{"pid":"b41bcd1efc86a7ffcd8fb3a40afcc4087fde1ad0","tid":2494563,"uid":42182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢停呀<br />\n繼續升市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83833945036d819f8a6b61a89239af59fd4b8e7d","tid":2494563,"uid":316048,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim